<i>Mrs. Pinky Benson to the crowd</i>.

1297
01:35:13,960 --> 01:35:16,428
<i>Oh, this is fabulous</i>.

1298
01:35:21,640 --> 01:35:22,959
<i>The crowd is roaring so much</i>.

1299
01:35:23,120 --> 01:35:25,156
<i>I hope you can hear me,</i>
<i>ladies and gentlemen</i>.

1300
01:35:25,320 --> 01:35:29,154
<i>I've never seen a premiere like this</i>.
<i>Now they're going into the theater</i>.

1301
01:35:29,680 --> 01:35:31,875
