01:35:42,080 --> 01:35:43,877
This is the greatest thing
you've done.

1307
01:35:44,040 --> 01:35:46,873
Pinky, I don't ever want to direct
another actor.

1308
01:35:47,040 --> 01:35:50,350
Thank you. Let's get rid of that creep.
I'll direct the next one myself.

1309
01:35:50,520 --> 01:35:53,273
This picture is a cinch to do
50 million at the box office.

1310
01:35:53,440 --> 01:35:55,510
