- Well.

1313
01:36:00,800 --> 01:36:04,554
Why should I carry those dead weights?
I'll play all four.

1314
01:36:04,720 --> 01:36:07,154
- He can do it too.
- Come on, let's get out of here.

1315
01:36:07,320 --> 01:36:10,278
