Everybody out of the way.

1316
01:36:11,280 --> 01:36:14,352
- All right.
- Mr. Benson, you was divine!

1317
01:36:14,520 --> 01:36:17,114
- Just divine!
- Now, coming to our cameras...

1318
01:36:17,280 --> 01:36:20,397
